author: giraffenmensch
body:
>large majority

Care to supply some numbers for this from a reputable source? The vast majority of cryptocurrency isn't even moved much. With Bitcoin, since all transactions are public, we've got perfect insight into the data, unlike with cash. So what percentage is used by criminals? What are their public keys?

The large majority of most crypto currencies is simply held by investors, traders and the likes.

author: SorrowsSkills
body:
For anyone interested, this is a simple list I made with some minor/vague notes on companies I want to look into that I found from this thread, felt I'd just put my personal favourites all into one spot for anyone looking.

StoneCo (online payment system in Brazil, Berkshire and Jack Ma invested)

SPLK disruptive company

TDOC disruptive health company

VEEV (cloud software for healthcare industry, very interesting)

SE (Sea Ltd) very interesting company based in southeast asia

WORK

TEAM (cloud software for the workplace)

GLPG (Pharma good growth, funded by Gilead, late stage clinical trials)

NET

SQ

AYX

LVGO (Pharma, don't understand)

HIMX (semiconductor)

KEYS

TTD (amazing advertising company, targets specific demographics, cheaper)

SPCE (ew)

PDD (China ecommerce but targets 3rd tier cities, gaining market share)

DKNG and Penn for online/sports betting

SDGR (Uses AI to develop new drugs (?), Bill Gates has a large position)

AMD (best CPUs now, moving for best GPU, potential for cloud servers)

ENPH (very hype, owns a lot of microinverter tech for solar panels, recently become profitable)

OKTA (identity and access management online for websites)

DDOG (cloud sciences used by Amazon, google and microsoft)

SEDG (solar energy company)

author: absoluteboredom
body:
Sex is great from what I hear. But very rarely is it worth the batshit aftermath. She goes through your phone while you sleep, sees a text from a girl and loses her shit, keys your car, throws your keys in the garbage disposal and tries to set your house on fire right after she cuffs your passed out ass to the bed. 

Didn’t happen to me, but it did happen to a close friend of mine. 

In lighter news he said she was an absolute animal in bed. Also, the text was from his mother asking how he was doing. But she was in another country and forgot about time difference.
